name: Beatiful Chaos
description:
We live in the same world and I believe what is happening near me is happening in your place too. life is like art, it cannot be defined but can be felt, everyone has full control over himself like an artist who has problems with his own art.

sometimes I think, I hate this life because of the complexity in it, but on the other hand I also love this life, I love being born as me and all its complications.

life is strange and unpredictable, life is sometimes fun but also annoying, life is a real paradox.
